metadata.name: Pecoz Boyz Motorcycle Club
metadata.description:
Postcard #1 by PurpleDrank 

Motorcycle meme clubs, sometimes called outlaw clubs, are what many people think of as the counterculture group of NFT PFPs. In part, these groups formed to go against the archaic origins of the PFP collection.

The PECOZ Boyz run the illegal $pepe trade in New Pecos. You in? Or out?
